                <h1>Hoof &#039;n&#039; Horn&#039;s &#039;Addams Family&#039; brings fresh talent to the Rubenstein </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/ff832698-7021-408d-ba2c-f90c9e36e91f.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Hoof&#x20;&#x27;n&#x27;&#x20;Horn&#x27;s&#x20;fall&#x20;show&#x20;features&#x20;ghoulish&#x20;makeup&#x20;and&#x20;costumes&#x20;in&#x20;addition&#x20;to&#x20;a&#x20;host&#x20;of&#x20;both&#x20;new&#x20;and&#x20;old&#x20;talent.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Hoof 'n' Horn's fall show features ghoulish makeup and costumes in addition to a host of both new and old talent.</p>

